msgid ""
"&konqueror;’s web browser functionality has its <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"khtml-behavior/index.html\">own configuration modules</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"A funcionalidade de &konqueror; como navegador web ten os seus propios "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/khtml-behavior/index.html\">módulos de "
"configuración</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Misc Options"
msgstr "Opcións diversas"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open folders in separate windows"
msgstr "Abrir os cartafoles en xanelas separadas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when "
#| "you open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder's contents in "
#| "the current window."
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when you "
"open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder’s contents in the "
"current window."
msgstr ""
"Se marca esta opción hase crear unha nova xanela de &konqueror; ao entrar "
"nun cartafol, en troques de usar a xanela actual para amosar o contido dese "
"cartafol."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Show 'Delete' menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgid "Show “Delete” menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgstr "Amosar entradas de «Eliminar» no menú que se saltan o lixo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be "
#| "displayed on the desktop and in the file manager's context menus. You can "
#| "always delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling "
#| "<guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be displayed "
"on the desktop and in the file manager’s context menus. You can always "
"delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling <guimenuitem>Move to "
"Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Marque isto se quere amosar as ordes do menú <quote>Eliminar</quote> no "
"escritorio e nos menús contextuais do xestor de ficheiros. Sempre ha poder "
"eliminar os ficheiros premendo a tecla &Shift; mentres escolle "
"<guimenuitem>Botar no lixo</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The settings for &konqueror;'s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
#| "Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
#| "guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> "
#| "pages are used by &dolphin; as well."
msgid ""
"The settings for &konqueror;’s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
"Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> pages "
"are used by &dolphin; as well."
msgstr ""
"A configuración do modo de xestión e ficheiros de &konqueror; nas páxinas de "
"<guilabel>Modos da vista</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navegación</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Servizos</guilabel>, <guilabel>Xeral</guilabel> e <guilabel>Lixo</"
"guilabel> tamén a usa &dolphin;."

